Ebiten - A 2D Game Library -


* Platform

- Mac OS X


* How to compile

You need:
- Xcode 4.2
- Boost
- Cocoa.framework (Mac OS X)
- OpenGL.framework (Mac OS X)
- QuartzCore.framework (Mac OS X)

Do 'make' command to create ebiten.app (a kind of a sample).


* Use on the Xcode (4.2)

- Add frameworks to 'Linked Frameworks and Libraries' (Mac OS X only)
  - OpenGL.framework
  - QuartzCore.framework
- Configure 'Build Setting'
  - 'User Header Search Path': /path/to/ebiten/src
  - 'C++ Language Dialect':    C++0x [-std=c++0x]
  - 'C++ Standard Library':    libc++ (LLVM C++ standard library with C++'0x support)
- Use kernel::start_with_view instead of kernel::main_loop


